{"tid":1615281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賴義士係咪聽日再提堂？","createTime":"2019-10-03T04:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T05:08:53.000Z","uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7907f67294e72f18a4d8421a109bf97b6b6959c1","tid":1615281,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=360158&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360158%26refer%3D&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=825f50dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360158%26refer%3D&h=c47a0231\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=360158&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】涉嫌襲擊《環球時報》記者的男子，另外被控在上月沙田警民衝突中襲警案件，在沙田裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n19歲被告賴雲龍由囚車押送至法院提堂。控罪指他於上月14日在沙田警民衝突中襲擊一名警長，辯方申請押後案件，索取控方文件及法律意見，裁判官將案件押後至10月4日再提堂。<br />\n<br />\n由於被告早前涉嫌襲擊《環球時報》記者付國豪，被控傷人罪、襲擊致造成身體傷害罪及參與非法集結罪，被告需還柙候訊"},{"pid":"e6699a214d4e696bd5a437863b1290141a6645a6","tid":1615281,"uid":218231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:08:53.000Z","msg":"係咪同一個？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mbouhjb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbouhjb.png&h=fccfb1c9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}